page.title: 12The Tupsley Area.
page.content:
The Tupsley area is predominantly residential . Many of the houses have been erected since the second World War and there two very new estates built in the last ten years.
The majority of the buildings are detached or semi-detached houses.Very few are terraced homes.
The older houses are concentrated near the bottom of Old Eign Hill, along the main Hampton Bishop road which runs parallel to the river.
A small industrial estate has grown near to the Hampton Bishop road but is restricted , because of the space available , to a dozen or so small businesses.
